fc: class Solution { public:     int findPeakElement(vector<int>& nums) {         int lo = 0, hi = nums.size() - 1;         while (lo < hi) {             int mid = (lo + hi) / 2;             if (nums[mid] < nums[mid + 1]) {                 lo = mid + 1;             } else {                 hi = mid;             }         }         return lo;     } };

fm: vector<int> twoSum(vector<int>& numbers, int target) {         int i = 0, j = numbers.size() - 1;         while (i < j) {             if (numbers[i] + numbers[j] < target) {                 i++;             } else if (numbers[i] + numbers[j] > target) {                 j--;             } else {                 return {i + 1, j + 1};             }         }         throw logic_error("Unreachable code path");     }

fm: int minSubArrayLen(int s, vector<int>& nums) {         vector<int> sum(nums.size() + 1);         for (int i = 1; i < sum.size(); i++) {             sum[i] = sum[i - 1] + nums[i - 1];         }         if (sum.back() <  s) return 0;         if (sum.back() == s) return nums.size();                  int min_len = nums.size() + 1;         for (int i = 0; i < sum.size() - 1; i++) {             int end = min(i + min_len, (int)sum.size());             for (int j = i + 1; j < end; j++) {                 if (sum[j] - sum[i] >= s) {                     min_len = j - i;                     break;                 }             }         }         return min_len;     }
